<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你<delay8 />前陣子
送花給我喔。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="4" />這沒什麼，不用道謝啦。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟我也經常<delay8 />
受你照顧嘛！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過話說回來，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />你送我風信子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且還是黃色的風信子<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊？<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />黃色的風信子<delay8 />
怎麼了嗎？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />黃色的風信子<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />花語是<delay frames="40" />「有你我就很幸福」<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />等、<20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等一下，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你說花語？<delay frames="40" />
我根本不知道<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那是什麼東西啊！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒關係！<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的沒關係啦，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不要緊，你別在意，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這我都知道！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">什、<delay20 /><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼，你說你知道什麼了！？<delay20 />
喂、<delay20 />喂！<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你聽到了嗎！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快回來啊～！！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說花啊，<delay8 />一定得考慮那麼多<delay8 />
才能送人嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早知道我就送個<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />之類的<delay8 />
就好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />你為什麼會<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送我菊花當禮物呢？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且居然<delay8 />還全部都是綠色的……<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">因為明明是花，<20_2 arg="4" />卻是綠色的啊！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想說這麼稀有的花，<delay20 />
你收到應該會很開心嘛<anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我說<20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
送禮物這種事，<delay20 />
可不是光看禮物很稀有就好了喔。<anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說，<delay20 />如果你收到看起來像<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />，<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />味道吃起來卻像<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />的食物，<delay8 />
<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />你會怎麼想呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算禮物本身再怎麼稀有，<delay20 />
收到這種禮物你應該也不會高興吧？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那是什麼！？<20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也太有趣了吧！！<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是那種禮物，<delay20 />
我倒是很樂意收下咧！<anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />總覺得<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />我們好像無法互相理解呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />算了，我也不多說了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
還是很謝謝你<delay20 />送花給我喔<anim id="Greeting" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，<delay20 />雖然我很常被周遭的人說<delay8 />
看起來很可怕啦。<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但到底是<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />可怕在哪裡啊？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />怎麼會突然問這個呢？<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="40" />
難道你很在意被別人說<delay8 />
看起來很可怕嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這其實沒什麼關係吧？<delay20 />
就算你的長相和說話方式很可怕，<anim id="Serious" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
我們也能像這樣<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />相處得很好呀。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" />雖然你嘴上說沒關係，<delay20 />
但原來你心裡也覺得我的長相<delay8 />
和說話方式很可怕啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><20_3 arg="8" />喂！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />，<20_2 arg="6" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那你覺得咧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">長相很可怕！</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">說話方式很可怕！</message>
	<message label="103_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="player" targetSpec="" />是的，一點都不可怕</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算<20_2 arg="2" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你說我長得很可怕，我也沒辦法啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
不然要怎麼辦嘛？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />與其說是長相，<20_2 arg="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="50" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如說是你的表情很可怕吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實你只要一直保持微笑就好了呀。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我來笑一個試試<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><20_2 arg="2" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣嗎？<20_3 arg="8" /><delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的表情<20_2 arg="3" />很僵硬呢。<anim id="ColdChill" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Sighing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />果然是說話方式的問題呢。<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="50" />
<20_2 arg="5" /><anim id="Serious" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />試著<20_2 arg="7" />多注意自己的語氣，
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說話的時候溫柔一點怎麼樣呢？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />溫柔嗎？<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，我了啦！<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不對，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我懂啦！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><10_4 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像也不對。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="8" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明白了！<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">總覺得<20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />你這樣說話<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然變得很卑躬屈膝呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看還是不要勉強比較好吧？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也對，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />哦！<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />不愧是<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟是咱倆這麼好的交情嘛！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這表示你看到了我的內在對吧！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />是說<20_2 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你剛才說話幹嘛對我這麼恭敬啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />所以就說<delay20 />
我根本沒在生氣了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />受不了──！<delay frames="40" />
為什麼<delay8 />我老是會被問<delay8 />
你是不是在生氣啊！<anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真不好意思<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="3" />，<delay8 />那是我誤會你了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay20 />你說話這麼粗魯又不親切的態度，<delay8 />
也有問題吧？<anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就算你這麼說，<20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我也沒辦法啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不然<delay20 />你那個叫「<tag a="110" b="6" />」的口頭禪，<delay8 />
借我用好啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼一來，<delay20 />我的語氣應該<delay8 />
也能變好一點吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果還是改不掉<20_2 arg="3" />自己的說話方式呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay20 />這樣才像<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的作風，<delay8 />
感覺也不錯<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>